<h2>AI and the Future of Google Reviews</h2>
<p>AI is changing how consumers discover and evaluate reviews. The 2026 data shows a dramatic shift.</p>
<p><strong>49. 45% of consumers now use AI tools like ChatGPT for business recommendations.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey/">BrightLocal, 2026</a>
This jumped from just 6% in 2025. AI-based discovery is growing at an extraordinary pace.</p>
<p><strong>50. 23% of consumers rely solely on AI-generated review summaries.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://www.brightlocal.com/research/local-consumer-review-survey/">BrightLocal, 2026</a>
