<p><strong>52. Google uses machine learning to detect and remove fraudulent reviews.</strong>
Source: <a href="https://support.google.com/business/answer/2622994">Google Support</a>
Google's automated systems scan for patterns that indicate fake reviews, paid reviews, and review manipulation.</p>
